{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"641c2ed5e9","title":"关于已向南京提出四项意见致叶剑英电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b1cbf0ba6a","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":14,"articleId":"641c2ed5e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"761af6d939","type":"paragraph","text":"关于已向南京提出四项意见致叶剑英电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"},{"id":"ed890b9fd8","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年10月14日）剑：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"},{"id":"7e64c74a2b","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、识延胡宗南进攻，使我在十一月十五日以前保持西兰大道于手中，以便二、四方面军休息整理，顺利执行新任务。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"},{"id":"65230a2a62","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、已向南京提出：第一，日寇进甚急，我方愿以全力为助，希望宁方坚持民族立场，不作任何丧权让步。第二，我方首先执行停止对国民党军队攻击，仅取防御方针，等候和议谈判集力抗日第三，欲图和议谈判早日实现，请将暂时以任何适当名义停止军队进攻，以便开始谈判，若一面进攻一面谈判，似无此理。第四，在进攻未停止、恩来未出去以前，准备派在沪之潘汉年同志进行初步谈判，此项请告毅\"并转年P","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"},{"id":"aceab548ac","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、年何日去沪，毅何日赴宁","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"},{"id":"b44716905f","type":"paragraph","text":"东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"},{"id":"91a2b3bc31","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十四日十六时[1]指张学良。[21指潘汉年。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9"}],"page":{"id":"5b30ca0c7a","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"641c2ed5e9","start":228,"end":228}}}},"__N_SSG":true}